Pour 1/4 cup of the dressing over chicken in shallow dish. Refrigerate 20 min. to marinate. Drain; discard marinade. Preheat grill to medium heat. Grill chicken 10 to 12 min. or until cooked through (170 degrees F), turning after 5 min. Cut into thin slices. Toss lettuce with remaining 1/4 cup dressing, chicken slices, croutons, bacon bits and cheese.